OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy on Saturday, the
OL,6,Fcloud bringing morning drizzle over
OL,7,Fthe hills before lifting to keep it
OL,8,Fdrier in the afternoon, perhaps with
OL,9,Fsome brighter spells. Temperatures
OL,10,Fslightly down on recently but still
OL,11,Frather warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOften cloudy with outbreaks
OL,14,Fof drizzle, some heavier bursts
OL,15,Fdeveloping chiefly over the hills
OL,16,Fbefore a general area of rain arrives
OL,17,Ffrom the south towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
