OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,6,Fthis locally heavy across the south of
OL,7,Fthe region. The rain breaking into
OL,8,Fshowers, perhaps thundery during the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Some brighter spells
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FShowers easing during Monday and
OL,14,FTuesday with sunnier spells emerging.
OL,15,FSimilar on Wednesday with variable
OL,16,Famounts of cloud, feeling chillier
OL,17,Fthan recent days as temperatures fall
OL,18,Faway.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
